summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2014 JEEP CHEROKEE. WHILE DRIVING APPROXIMATELY 60 MPH, THE SUN ROOF EXPLODED OUTWARD. THERE WERE NO INJURIES. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO RICK HENDRICKS COLLISION CENTER (LOCATED ON 1535 SAVANNAH HWY CHARLESTON, SC 29407), BUT WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE AND VIN WERE UNKNOWN.
